John Markoff is a senior writer for {\i
The New York Times} who has coauthored {\i
Cyberpunk: Outlaws and Hackers on the Computer Frontier} and the bestselling {\i
Takedown: The Pursuit and Capture of Kevin Mitnick, America\uc1\u8217's Most Wanted Computer Outlaw}. He lives in San Francisco, California. }
